Design and implement a complete enterprise-grade Data Visualization Engine from scratch for a React + FastAPI application (Chillview), replacing the existing chart builder and chart recommender system entirely, while preserving the existing Org Chart implementation.

The system must support the following chart types:

BAR, LINE, AREA, PIE, DONUT, SCATTER, BUBBLE, HEATMAP, TREEMAP, SUNBURST, COMBO_BAR_LINE, GAUGE, SPARKLINE, RADAR, KPI_SINGLE, TABLE

---

1. CORE ARCHITECTURE

Build a modular architecture with the following layers:

Frontend (React):

* Chart Builder Panel
* Field Assignment System
* Chart Renderer (ECharts)
* Chart Recommendation Engine UI

Backend (FastAPI):

* Data profiling API
* Aggregation engine
* Chart recommendation API
* Analytics computation endpoints (/hr/analytics/*)

---

2. COLUMN PROFILING ENGINE

Automatically classify dataset columns into:

* DIMENSION (categorical → string, enums)
* MEASURE (numeric → int, float)
* TIME (date/datetime)
* IDENTIFIER (unique IDs like employee_id)

Rules:

* If unique > 95% → mark as IDENTIFIER
* If numeric → MEASURE
* If date → TIME
* Else → DIMENSION

Return metadata:
{
column_name,
type: "dimension" | "measure" | "time" | "id",
unique_count,
null_count,
sample_values
}

---

3. CHART CONFIGURATION MODEL

Each chart must strictly define required fields:

BAR:

* X Axis: DIMENSION
* Y Axis: MEASURE (aggregation required)

LINE:

* X Axis: TIME (preferred) OR DIMENSION
* Y Axis: MEASURE

AREA:

* Same as LINE

PIE / DONUT:

* Category: DIMENSION
* Value: MEASURE (COUNT default)

SCATTER:

* X: MEASURE
* Y: MEASURE

BUBBLE:

* X: MEASURE
* Y: MEASURE
* Size: MEASURE

HEATMAP:

* X: DIMENSION
* Y: DIMENSION
* Value: MEASURE

TREEMAP / SUNBURST:

* Hierarchy: MULTI DIMENSION
* Value: MEASURE

COMBO_BAR_LINE:

* X: DIMENSION or TIME
* Y1: MEASURE (bar)
* Y2: MEASURE (line)

GAUGE:

* Value: SINGLE MEASURE

SPARKLINE:

* TIME + MEASURE

RADAR:

* DIMENSION + MULTIPLE MEASURES

KPI_SINGLE:

* SINGLE MEASURE

TABLE:

* ANY fields

---

4. FIELD ASSIGNMENT PANEL (CRITICAL UX)

Replace current system with:

Sections:

* DIMENSION (X Axis / Category)
* MEASURE (Values)
* TIME (Optional)
* SIZE (for bubble)
* COLOR / LEGEND

Rules:

* Only allow compatible fields per chart
* Disable invalid selections
* Show helper text:

Example:
"Bar Chart requires 1 Dimension + 1 Measure"

Auto suggestions:

* Auto-fill best fields when chart selected

---

5. AGGREGATION ENGINE (VERY IMPORTANT)

Auto-assign aggregations:

* ID → COUNT ONLY
* Numeric → SUM / AVG
* Default:

  * COUNT for dimensions
  * SUM for measures

Prevent:

* SUM(employee_id)
* AVG(string)

---

6. CHART RECOMMENDATION ENGINE

Build a scoring system:

Input:

* #dimensions
* #measures
* #time columns

Rules:

1 dimension + 1 measure → BAR (score 90)
1 time + 1 measure → LINE (95)
2 measures → SCATTER (85)
1 dimension + many measures → RADAR (75)
hierarchy fields → TREEMAP/SUNBURST (80)
any measure → KPI / GAUGE (60)

Return ranked list:
[
{ chart: "bar", score: 90 },
{ chart: "pie", score: 75 }
]

Auto-select top result.

---

7. ENTERPRISE CHART DESIGN (VERY IMPORTANT)

All charts must include:

* Title + Subtitle
* Axis labels
* Data labels (intelligent visibility)
* Tooltips (rich)
* Legends (scrollable if large)
* Grid spacing optimized
* Responsive layout
* Export-ready styling

Export requirements:

* PNG/PDF must include:

  * labels
  * readable fonts
  * no overlap
  * high DPI

